[section {Command Reference}]

The database API is documented in separate command manpages:

[list_begin itemized]

[item] Command [cmd ns_db]:
Database access API for obtaining handles, executing SQL, iterating over
result rows, transaction handling, and related database operations.

[item] Command [cmd ns_buildsqldate]:
SQL date and time manipulation commands.

[item] Command [cmd ns_dbquotevalues]:
Quote database names and values for use in SQL statements.

[list_end]

